Package SimulationFramework

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Drawable
    Drawable interfaces must implement public Draw(Graphics G).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnimatePanel
    AnimatePanel is the GUI component of the simulation framework package.
    Bot
    Bot is an abstract class for any "player" or "robot" subclass that will be controlled by a path-finding and/or a moving algorithm().
    Connector
    Connector is used to draw lines between points on the simulation's canvas.
    Marker
    Markers are used to represent position on the canvas that Bot's can use for path finding.
    SimFrame
    An abstract class for the framework's GUI.
